Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.19,0:09:18.45,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}you know here's b in I’ll just slide it down there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:18.45,Chi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个是B，我把它放到这个位置
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.45,0:09:22.48,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}uh but then you have to put A and you	 can kind of see where it goes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:22.48,Chi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但然后你放A进去，你可以看它的位置
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.48,0:09:27.09,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}right like it's kind of kind of wrap around there and slide in there but you just you can't slide it in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:27.09,Chi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它有点像把它包裹住了，放不进去
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.82,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}there's no way to make it work
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.82,Chi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样也不行
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.82,0:09:32.47,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}so, it's not A before B and it's not B before A
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:32.47,Chi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，既不是先放A再放B，也不是先放B再放A
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.47,0:09:34.20,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}well then it must be impossible, right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:34.20,Chi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么这一定是不可能的，对吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.20,0:09:39.70,Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}but no actually the solution is you take B and you put it in kind of halfway and you stick it up there
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:39.70,Chi,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但不是的，实际上解法是你把B放到一半，然后就先不动它
